Third-party acknowledgements
============================

Kotoforge does NOT bundle, copy, or adapt any third-party source code.
It relies on the following external tools and services at runtime; each
remains under its own license and is not redistributed in this repository:

- Semantic Scholar — academic metadata (title, authors, year, DOI, venue)
  used by the `citation-reference-management` skill to verify and complete
  references. Data via the Semantic Scholar API (Allen Institute for AI).
  https://www.semanticscholar.org/

- semantic-scholar-mcp — MCP server invoked through `.mcp.json` to reach the
  Semantic Scholar API. External dependency, not part of this repo.
  https://github.com/akapet00/semantic-scholar-mcp

- Pandoc — Markdown ⇄ Word (.docx) conversion (`markdown-to-word` skill).

- Python libraries — PyMuPDF, pdfplumber, python-docx, mammoth, pypandoc
  (`source-document-extraction` and `markdown-to-word` skills).

Bibliographic metadata retrieved from Semantic Scholar is factual reference
data about publications, used for citation verification only.
